title: José Albuquerque
text: José Anastácio de Albuquerque (born December 7, 1975 in <a href="Senador%20Jos%C3%A9%20Porf%C3%ADrio">Senador José Porfírio</a>, <a href="Par%C3%A1">Pará</a>) is a Brazilian <a href="Boxing">boxer</a>, who represented his native country in the <a href="flyweight">flyweight</a> division at the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%202000%20Summer%20Olympics">2000 Summer Olympics</a> in <a href="Sydney%2C%20Australia">Sydney, Australia</a>. There he was eliminated in the first round by <a href="Ukraine">Ukraine</a>'s <a href="Valeriy%20Sydorenko">Valeriy Sydorenko</a>.
